{
  "total_duration": 772.643,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 8.904,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Out of the darkness"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“冲出黑暗”。但这不是恐怖故事，也不是鼓励大家去冒险。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 9.254,
      "end": 29.353,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "它是一条 survival route，求生路线：一个女孩从"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "出发，遇到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "storm"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，船撞到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，她跳进"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sea"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，游了一整夜，最后看见"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "light ahead"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 29.703,
      "end": 41.895,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这盏灯很关键。它不是装饰，它在高高的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cliffs"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "上，告诉她：land is near, the shore is near, safety is near。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 42.245,
      "end": 55.725,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把现代安全桥说清楚：今天如果出海，要看天气预报，穿救生衣，带能联系人的设备，最好有 GPS 和 location sharing，不要一个人靠勇气硬撑。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 56.074,
      "end": 69.474,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里的女孩很坚强，但我们学习的不是模仿危险行为。我们学习的是：danger -> no clear direction -> find a signal -> move toward safety -> recover。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 69.824,
      "end": 90.611,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课还要先看一张小地图："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是海边一带，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "shore"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是水和陆地接触的岸边，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是海里的危险礁石，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cliff"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是海边很高很陡的峭壁，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ahead"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是在前方。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 90.961,
      "end": 108.993,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天背诵就抓住这条路线："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "storm"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sea"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whole night"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "eight miles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "light"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cliffs"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "->"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "hospital"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 109.342,
      "end": 117.374,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，从时间差开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Nearly a week passed before the girl was able to explain what had happened to her."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 117.724,
      "end": 125.956,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她不是马上就能讲清楚。她经历了危险，休息和恢复之后，才说出"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "what had happened to her"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 126.306,
      "end": 132.618,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后故事回到那天下午："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "One afternoon she set out from the coast in a small boat."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 132.968,
      "end": 141.864,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "set out from"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是从某地出发，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是海岸地区，不只是脚边一小块沙子。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 142.213,
      "end": 155.229,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "同一句里危险来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "and was caught in a storm"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was caught in a storm"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“被人抓住”，而是突然陷入风暴，很难逃开。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 155.579,
      "end": 162.979,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "画面里要看见：小船很小，海很大，天气开始变坏。This is not a safe plan today."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 163.329,
      "end": 171.433,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，时间往傍晚推："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Towards evening, the boat struck a rock and the girl jumped into the sea."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 171.783,
      "end": 180.519,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Towards evening"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是接近傍晚，天色越来越暗。这个时间很重要，因为黑暗会让方向更难判断。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 180.869,
      "end": 193.588,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "struck a rock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是路边小石头，而是海里的危险礁石。小船撞上去，就可能出大问题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 193.938,
      "end": 204.818,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "女孩跳进海里，这不是英雄动作，而是在危险中求生。我们不要把她画成 superhero，也不要把画面做成吓人的 disaster scene。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 205.168,
      "end": 215.712,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到这里，路线变成："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "出发，风暴中撞到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rock"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，然后进入"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sea"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 216.062,
      "end": 224.485,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，是整课最难也最重要的一段："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then she swam to the shore after spending the whole night in the water."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 224.835,
      "end": 233.019,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "after spending the whole night in the water"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "要读成一整块：她不是游一会儿，而是在水里度过了整整一夜。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 233.369,
      "end": 244.553,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文继续说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "During that time she covered a distance of eight miles."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "covered a distance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里是“走过或游过一段距离”，不是“盖住”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 244.903,
      "end": 251.487,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到第二天清晨，转折出现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Early next morning, she saw a light ahead."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 251.836,
      "end": 258.844,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "ahead"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是在她前方，在她移动的方向上。这个 light 给了她 direction。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 259.194,
      "end": 268.434,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这幅画要安静一点：夜海之后，远处高处有灯。The darkness is still there, but now she has a way to move."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 268.784,
      "end": 276.32,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画，把灯和陆地连起来："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She knew she was near the shore because the light was high up on the cliffs."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 276.67,
      "end": 289.022,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "shore"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是她终于能到达陆地的水边；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cliffs"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是岸边高高陡陡的峭壁。灯在高处，所以她知道陆地就在附近。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 289.372,
      "end": 297.068,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着是最后一次努力："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "On arriving at the shore, the girl struggled up the cliff towards the light she had seen."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 297.417,
      "end": 306.657,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "On arriving at the shore"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是 when she arrived at the shore；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "struggled up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是非常吃力地往上爬。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 307.007,
      "end": 315.759,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the light she had seen"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是她之前看到的那盏灯。先 saw the light，后来 struggled towards the same light。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 316.109,
      "end": 320.437,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后记忆断在这里："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "That was all she remembered."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 320.787,
      "end": 331.882,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "结尾很轻："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she woke up a day later, she found herself in hospital."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她醒来时发现自己在医院里，说明她已经被救助，正在安全恢复。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 332.232,
      "end": 335.656,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课为什么叫"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Out of the darkness"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 336.006,
      "end": 338.693,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为她真的在黑夜里的海里？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 339.043,
      "end": 347.723,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，这是第一层，literal darkness，真的黑暗。还有第二层：她没有方向，也不知道离岸还有多远。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 348.073,
      "end": 352.404,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "light ahead"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么这么重要？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 352.754,
      "end": 363.586,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为光在前方，而且在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cliffs"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "上。它告诉她：那里有陆地，有方向，有希望。The light turns fear into a route."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 363.936,
      "end": 369.881,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "shore"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我总分不清。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 370.231,
      "end": 383.239,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样记："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "coast"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是海边一大片地区，比如 coastal city；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "shore"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是水碰到陆地的边。她从 coast 出发，最后游到 shore。"
        }
      ]
    },
