    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 386.595,
      "end": 396.699,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cliff"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是很高、很陡的岩壁，不是普通小山坡。灯在 cliff 上，所以她从水里能看见高处的 light。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 397.049,
      "end": 399.594,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这故事听起来很危险。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 399.944,
      "end": 413.944,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是的，所以现代桥一定要说清楚。今天我们会用 weather forecast, life jacket, phone, GPS, emergency call, location sharing。课文讲的是求生和方向，不是让人去冒险。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 414.294,
      "end": 425.934,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "背诵时把它当成 route map：from the coast, into the storm, into the sea, through the night, towards the light, up the cliff, and safe in hospital."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 426.284,
      "end": 431.132,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Nearly a week passed before the girl was able to explain what had happened to her."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 431.482,
      "end": 436.402,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "One afternoon she set out from the coast in a small boat and was caught in a storm."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 436.751,
      "end": 441.215,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Towards evening, the boat struck a rock and the girl jumped into the sea."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 441.565,
      "end": 445.669,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then she swam to the shore after spending the whole night in the water."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 446.019,
      "end": 449.619,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "During that time she covered a distance of eight miles."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 449.969,
      "end": 453.233,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Early next morning, she saw a light ahead."
